{"tid":121610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[傑出華人系列] 斬斷小狗四腳掌　強國餐廳毒招防逃走 (冇圖)","createTime":"2017-02-15T11:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T15:32:54.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1211f84264b57bb0763ae51af8c8d4d79db9302","tid":121610,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"真的太兇殘！近日內地多地餐館和市場，被揭為防用來上桌或出售的狗狗逃走，竟狠狠地砍去牠們四隻腳掌，血腥的照片曝光後，燃起了一眾網民的怒火！<br />\n<br />\n動物保護團體「Guardians of Chinese Animal Protection守護者」前日在facebook專頁中，PO出了兩張令人看後想落淚的照片，<span style=\"color: red;\">相中一隻可愛的拉布拉多幼犬，四隻腳的腳掌全被人砍去</span>，無法走動的牠就躺在一處爛地上，眼神無助而哀傷。該動保團體指，是在河北省三河市一個市場發現這隻小狗，當時牠正在待售中，估計行兇者是為防牠逃走，而切除其四肢。所幸該小狗已獲愛護動物人士救出，目前正在當地獸醫診所醫治，其後續情況將繼續在專頁發佈。<br />\n該動保團體還指，上月底時，中國一些餐館也揭將狗隻四肢斬去，至少收到2宗來自不同城市的個案。其中1宗個案是發生在天津市，當地網民於1月27日（年三十）發微博稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">一間餐館老闆將一隻黑色拉布拉多犬的四腳腳筋斬斷，愛護動物人士得悉後，以500元人民幣買下牠，並送到獸醫診所。當時其頭部也有受傷，獸醫診所免費為牠醫治。然而，當愛護動物人士報警時，公安竟指無法阻止任何人殺狗。</span><br />\n<br />\n另一宗案件的事發地點不詳，但據網民指，是一間火鍋店的老闆在屠宰場買了一隻狗狗，為怕牠逃跑，硬是砍了牠的一條腿。狗狗雙眼充滿絕望，見有人靠近，就會發出驚恐的嗚咽聲音，似乎在懇求人不要靠近牠，但火鍋店老闆對此卻無動於衷，有好心人願意出錢相救，卻被拒絕。據悉，狗狗已經死亡。<br />\n不少網民在看到有關貼文和照片後，都表示傷心和憤怒，難以相信在文明社會會出現這種殘忍的事件，直斥那些行兇者是有虐待狂的怪物！"},{"pid":"74012ebe42f5cc25443147e204e9403dd6cf4cc6","tid":121610,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"留名睇人話弱肉強食之後又世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d39af45e4986edc65ca06d13c7139e25ece0333","tid":121610,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇人話弱肉強食之後又世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食豬會唔會咁食呀"},{"pid":"ee15e36410cbbc0aa9632d53a14994cf5ef8b544","tid":121610,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名睇人話弱肉強食之後又世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食豬會唔會咁食呀</blockquote><br />\n唔理啦<br />\n總之食豬食牛，但屌人食狗就係偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b244afd32d7e9c55dee5190371210e738d0e791e","tid":121610,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"拉布拉多都食?<br />\n利申:咁講真咩狗都唔應該食,但拉布拉多都食就更加令人嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf320a8511e32939f6262eada7afff935f4f060","tid":121610,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"食狗唔係問題，但唔應該刻意咁虐待佢。完！"},{"pid":"b6325abf7dc616e5c94943f4f9a70aab9195a761","tid":121610,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:05:22.000Z","msg":".jpg?"},{"pid":"84dfb1599891a198b47421211e15505c8c16d8e6","tid":121610,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"有無睇過麥樂雞點炸"},{"pid":"0440662335e025a61940068d2d6fe060c93feefc","tid":121610,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"食蕃狗咁富貴?"},{"pid":"eb862a98cf503bba371ce915dcb2281fd72c220c","tid":121610,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食狗唔係問題，但唔應該刻意咁虐待佢。完！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489d040769b88232801f230b3a182c651494b79e","tid":121610,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名睇人話弱肉強食之後又世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食豬會唔會咁食呀</blockquote><br />\n唔理啦<br />\n總之食豬食牛，但屌人食狗就係偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地連登手足一向支持食狗,中間過程係點根本唔重要,最重要過口癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2447f90ca5bb9244814db376b4b749235f900ab","tid":121610,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食狗唔係問題，但唔應該刻意咁虐待佢。完！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無見過養雞場養豬場係咩環境同點整死佢地"},{"pid":"17fb693490deec4510493925b0e47f103b3254b8","tid":121610,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"其實而家大陸仲多唔多人食狗<br />\n見到有D大陸人都已經開始反食狗"},{"pid":"82c883c258ef67a38f16fb69a24f722f4d0450fb","tid":121610,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"好想知狗狗前世做左咩錯事搞到今世要投胎做支那狗咁慘"},{"pid":"f8307ed9a164319327f3aed2144848d20fc57ea3","tid":121610,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"狗狗已獲救同好返了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cd05bd5ae1b00cfd1e8ceadb32682f7a66f1bf","tid":121610,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T19:11:55.000Z","msg":"唔係再同生番講寵物貓狗<br />\n食狗殺狗虐待動物係黃皮狗本質黎"},{"pid":"7d99cc6e82e30201c93b2298c55f978f7eb19c08","tid":121610,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T19:13:59.000Z","msg":"野蠻民族講道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌咪傻啦，西方價值觀係套唔到落東南亞架"},{"pid":"a8c6eccb9dcceaee14ec5a53364e94ca6497f74b","tid":121610,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T20:43:46.000Z","msg":"我要做model"},{"pid":"6d22a